    "chapter": {
        "bookTitle": "3 Nephi",
        "delineation": "Chapter",
        "number": 25,
        "summary": "At the Second Coming, the proud and wicked will be burned as stubble\u2014Elijah will return before that great and dreadful day\u2014Compare Malachi 4. About A.D.\u00a034.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "For behold, the day cometh that shall burn as an oven; and all the proud, yea, and all that do wickedly, shall be stubble; and the day that cometh shall burn them up, saith the Lord of Hosts, that it shall leave them neither root nor branch.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Mal. 4:1 (1\u20136).",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 3
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 21:9 (8\u201310); Isa. 24:6; 66:16; 1\u00a0Ne. 22:15; 3\u00a0Ne. 24:2; D&C 29:9; 64:23 (23\u201324); 133:64; JS\u2014H 1:37. TG\u00a0Earth, Cleansing of.",
                        "start": 38,
                        "end": 42
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 18:27; 2\u00a0Ne. 20:33. TG\u00a0Pride.",
                        "start": 67,
                        "end": 72
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "But unto you that fear my name, shall the Son of Righteousness arise with healing in his wings; and ye shall go forth and grow up as calves in the stall.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ps. 84:11; Mal. 4:2; Ether 9:22.",
                        "start": 42,
                        "end": 62
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 45:58.",
                        "start": 122,
                        "end": 129
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Amos 6:4; 1\u00a0Ne. 22:24.",
                        "start": 133,
                        "end": 139
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And ye shall tread down the wicked; for they shall be ashes under the soles of your feet in the day that I shall do this, saith the Lord of Hosts.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "3\u00a0Ne. 21:12.",
                        "start": 13,
                        "end": 18
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Remember ye the law of Moses, my servant, which I commanded unto him in Horeb for all Israel, with the statutes and judgments.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 3:1; 19:18 (9, 16\u201320); 1\u00a0Kgs. 19:8; Neh. 9:13; Mosiah 12:33; 13:5.",
                        "start": 72,
                        "end": 77
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Behold, I will send you Elijah the prophet before the coming of the great and dreadful day of the Lord;",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "2\u00a0Kgs. 2:2; D&C 2:1; 35:4; 110:13 (13\u201316); 128:17 (17\u201318). TG\u00a0Genealogy and Temple Work.",
                        "start": 24,
                        "end": 30
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Day of the Lord.",
                        "start": 87,
                        "end": 90
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And he shall turn the heart of the fathers to the children, and the heart of the children to their fathers, lest I come and smite the earth with a curse.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 98:16 (16\u201317).",
                        "start": 13,
                        "end": 17
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Family, Eternal; Salvation for the Dead.",
                        "start": 35,
                        "end": 42
                    },
                    {
